---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import FooterEng from '../../components/en-components/FooterEng.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About Me" description="A look behind the scenes - who I am, what I do, and what drives me." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="about-section">
      <section>
        <h1 class="subpage-heading">About Me</h1>
        <p class="subpage-desc">
          Hi! I'm Jasmin - creative whirlwind, web nerd, competitive shooter, and mountain kid. <br />
          I love diving into new projects, creating things that are both beautiful and functional,
          and connecting with people who are passionate about what they do.
        </p>

        <p>
          In my everyday life, very different worlds collide: <strong>digital design</strong> meets
          <strong>competitive shooting</strong>, <strong>hiking</strong> meets <strong>content strategy</strong>,
          <strong>political theory</strong> meets <strong>Instagram captions</strong>. And somehow, it all fits - at least for me.
        </p>

        <p>
          I believe that good work can be fun. And that clarity, honesty, and humor
          are often the best ways to make complex things understandable.
        </p>

        <p>
          When I’m not tweaking lines of code or aligning layouts down to the pixel,
          I’m probably at the shooting range, on a mountain, or out with my camera somewhere.
        </p>

        <div class="facts-grid">
          <div><strong>📍 Hometown:</strong> Kufstein, Tyrol</div>
          <div><strong>🧠 Studies:</strong> Political Science</div>
		  <div><strong>🎓 Degree:</strong> BSc. Computer Science</div>
          <div><strong>🎯 Disciplines:</strong> Air rifle, smallbore & bigbore</div>
		  <div><strong>🏅 Biggest Achievement:</strong> 2nd place Air Rifle Mixed, World Cup Jakarta</div>
          <div><strong>💬 Languages:</strong> German, English, Italian, French</div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <FooterEng />
  </body>
</html>


<style lang="scss">
.about-section {
  width: 80%;
  max-width: 1600px;
  margin: 0 auto;



  .subpage-desc {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .facts-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
	  border: 0.2rem solid #fff;
	  border-radius: 16px;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;

    div {
      background: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-card);
    }
  }
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-section .facts-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(1,1fr);
  }

}
</style>
